title: Fresh on Spadina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Canadian
description: Natural food restaurant locations in Toronto. Menu features an array of starters, multi-layered salads, wraps, high protein burgers, and signature bowls. No dairy, eggs, honey, or animal by-products in the cooking; however, dairy is offered as a side option throughout the menu. Weekend brunch served til 3pm.
